<h2>Success Stories</h2>

<p class="content">Just for kicks, we're listing here the known
deployments of Microraptor (or, rather, those whose maintainers have
given us permission to do so), along with a few fun stats.</p>

<table border="0" class="content">
  <tr>
    <td class="head">Project</td>
    <td class="head">Processes</td>
    <td class="head">Machines</td>
    <td class="head">Affiliation</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="shortCell"><a href="http://www.frc.ri.cmu.edu/atacama/">Life in the
      Atacama</a></td>
    <td class="shortCell">55</td>
    <td class="shortCell">4</td>
    <td><a href="http://www.frc.ri.cmu.edu">Field Robotics Center</a>,
    <a href="http://www.ri.cmu.edu">Robotics Institute</a>, <a href="http://www.cmu.edu">Carnegie
      Mellon University</a></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
